  <p>What is that one thing without which your morning routine isn’t complete? 
What is it which lifts you up when tired and sleepy? 
Well, it even cures cold, cough as well as is tasty for you to always ask more of it. 
It comes in different variants: Ginger, Cardamom, Irani, Black, the list is endless.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>I don’t think I need to tell what is it, but in case you are still wondering, it’s <em>Tea</em>.</p>

<p>Today, in this article, let’s learn how to make a good cup of tea and how you can adjust it to your needs as required. Let’s get started, shall we?</p>

<h3 id="ingredient-list">Ingredient List</h3>
<ul>
  <li>100ml water</li>
  <li>300ml milk</li>
  <li>1tbsp tea leaves</li>
  <li>1tbsp sugar</li>
  <li>1 cardamom</li>
  <li>1 inch ginger</li>
  <li>Love ♥️</li>
</ul>

